con_aa <- df_c %>% select(group, y) %>% group_by(group, y) %>%
  summarise(count=n()) %>% pivot_wider(names_from = y, values_from = count) %>%
  mutate(cnt = no+yes) %>%
  mutate(con_rate = yes/cnt*100) %>%
  arrange(group)
